### React / Frontend
- Functional components only — no class components
- Custom hooks (use* prefix) for all reusable logic and data fetching
- TypeScript: strict mode, always typed props interfaces
- State: useState for local UI, React Query for all server data
- No prop drilling beyond 2 levels — use context or React Query
- CSS variables for theming — never hardcoded color values
- Lazy loading via React.lazy() + Suspense for route-level components
